node.text:
Platinum #Ford #F150 by @thedieselcartel. Lowered on our 24” Vossen HF6-2 in Silver Polished. This Wheel is designed and engineered specifically for trucks and SUVs, making it a perfect fit for any newer Ford F-150.

The HF6-2 is available in 20", 22" and 24" Diameters. 5 standard and 9 custom finishes, starting at $649 per wheel.

sales@vossenwheels.com / +1(305)463-7778 

Film/Edit: @Dela_vossen

node.title: PLATINUM FORD F-150 • HYBRID FORGED HF6-2

node.text:
No one has pushed the #CorvetteC8 to its limits more than @GabeFlorido, or as he is more widely known, @CarLifestyle. Gabe's C8 has been wrapped, lowered, modified and is currently sitting on our Vossen Forged S17-01, 3-Piece wheels. 

Take a look at a day in the life of @GabeFlorido and see what it's taken to get his C8 to where it is today. Thanks to @racingsportconcepts, @kw_suspension, @kooksheaders, and @fabspeed_motorsport for being a part of this build. 

Wheel Specs: 
20x9.5 / 21x12.5

Video: @dela_vossen

node.title: VOSSEN OWNER SPOTLIGHT • CAR LIFESTYLE'S GABE FLORIDO • CORVETTE C8
